sequenceDiagram
    participant F as Freelancer
    participant HUD as UI HUD (BiddingEditor)
    participant NC as Nexus Core (3D Scene)
    participant DB as Supabase (PostgreSQL)
    participant O as Organization

    Note over F, NC: Discovery Phase
    F->>NC: Interacts with 3D Starfield
    NC->>F: Visual Feedback (Hover/Select)
    F->>HUD: Opens Mission Details

    Note over HUD, DB: Bidding Phase
    F->>HUD: Enters Bid (Amount ₹ + Message)
    HUD->>HUD: Validates Inputs
    HUD->>DB: INSERT INTO bids (mission_id, freelancer_id, amount)
    DB-->>HUD: Confirm Success
    HUD->>F: Display Success Notification (Sonner)

    Note over DB, O: Management Phase
    DB->>O: Real-time update (RLS filter)
    O->>DB: Reviews Bids
    O->>F: Initiates "Connection" (Contract Negotiation)
